@database Scanner_Toaster.guide

@node Main "Scanner:  Toaster"

   The Toaster scanner module is used to transfer images directly from the
   Video Toaster framebuffers to ImageFX.

   @{u}Field:@{uu}  Number of fields to grab or "Motion Remove" to enable motion
      removal.

   @{u}Bank:@{uu}  Framestore Bank to grab from (DV1 or DV2).

   @{u}Transfer:@{uu}  Transfer data from Video Toaster framebuffer to
      ImageFX using the current settings.

@endnode

